My first attempt I just kinda hoped I wouldnâ€™t need recursion. It was silly, but a guy can dream. My next idea was to just create the file system and so thatâ€™s what I did. Rather than making the files the size it says, I just filled them with one line holding the size so that I could read it in later. Getting the instructions fleshed out wasnâ€™t too bad. It reminds me a lot of my Cat Simulator 2019 project from Intro to UNIX.

